  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "A pre-trained Ensemble Learning Neural Network model was created in the study by Kuo et al (2021) using student data from the most recent academic years and course results as training data.",
    "The K-means technique was used to classify all of the first through fourth grade courses so that they would all have the same characteristics and could be placed together in one cluster to increase prediction accuracy.",
    "Then, distinct neural networks were built for each course in accordance with the various academic years.",
    "Furthermore, using a de-noising auto-encoder, each model was pre-trained.",
    "The relevant structure and weights were used as the initial values of the neural network model after pre-training."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "A pre-trained Ensemble Learning Neural Network model was created in the study by Kuo et al (2021) using student data from the most recent academic years and course results as training data."
  ]
}